org.interledger.codecs.packettypes.InterledgerPacketType

  • InterledgerPacketTypeを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.interledger.codecs
    This package holds all codecs for the Interledger project, including top-level interfaces and abstract classes that can be utilized to create more specific codecs, such as for ASN.1 OER, JSON, Protobuf, and more.
